Package edu.uiuc.ncsa.security.storage

Interface ListeningStoreInterface<V extends Identifiable>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractListeningStore
    public interface ListeningStoreInterface<V extends Identifiable>
    Part of the event mechanism for tracking the last access time of store objects. This is used in OA4MP but has to be here for Java package visibility.
